Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:38.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不會向悲傷低頭的勇氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:44.25,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}為了保護珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:49.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我相信自己的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:55.52,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Saving our future  讓我們一同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}敞開明天的門  向開闊的天空
