Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  鐵裝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:35.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是暑假了還真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:38.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有工作沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:42.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到這個時候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天那邊也有工作嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:48.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:50.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:51.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  現在不是在意這種事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:00:58.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:01.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多加小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:05.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:14.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:30.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是盛大的遲到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:11.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每逢暑假學生都會很浮躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:19.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為光靠風紀委員很難維持風紀才需要我們出場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:19.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:21.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你都那麼浮躁怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:24.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是黃泉川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶劫？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的失敗就靠工作補償回來  明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:36.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃…黃泉川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢靠近我就殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我快把嫌犯給…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:44.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:45.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:47.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:01.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  能得高分數不是很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:03.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真能幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會輸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:11.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人質救出來就鬆懈了才會遇到那種事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此也用不著連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分數更新了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:19.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同學好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到完全放學時間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:29.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了就要靠工作補償回來不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我要全力以赴了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的不是全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先說好了別用踢的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯規可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到完全放學時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回家裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:52.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:57.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次實在承蒙關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此  謝謝你們能出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  您好像稍微瘦了點？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:08.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如說憔悴了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:09.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:13.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還是應該好好保養一下皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備員還真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:19.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:22.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把這些壓力發洩到這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:24.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還在工作崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定對皮膚有好處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我試試吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟著玩怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你們也快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:37.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的可怕的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那邊的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是完全放學時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:44.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鴻野江
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:51.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同班同學  雖然不那麼熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為感覺讓人比較難接近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:05.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙燙燙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滲進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了鐵裝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  熱水滲進擦傷的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近很不正常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:23.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是  一會兒遲到一會被當作人質還上學生的當
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:24.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說之前算不上是很優秀的警備員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太過鬆懈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:39.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣  在工作一天之後泡的澡最舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萌老師也是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  我要烤雞胗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:55.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:03.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟往常一樣能喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵裝  我們繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:06.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:08.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}大叔  再來一瓶酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:08.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:10.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  你的弱點是太懦弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}還有烤芋頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我鼓起勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:12.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作起來才能贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  要振作振作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:22.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  來份烤肝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:25.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作起來…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:42.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的巡邏是從A區到D區
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分開進行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎鐵裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是北面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟媽媽是在哪裏走散的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是不順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  馬上就到完全放學時間了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激掌9
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園都市裏居然這麼老的遊戲也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候常常玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是沒出10呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我說你  快點回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:54.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  來份豬肘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:32.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要一份牛背和竹筍片生魚片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:32.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說鐵裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:37.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼煩惱可以跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說不上是煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼總是失誤不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:54.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  人生苦短  戀愛吧少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了鐵裝  你有什麼興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  不算興趣也行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也可以做一下自己喜歡的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:07.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天能讓女性變成獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:08.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉變一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:11.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以  放開束縛  盡情地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情地…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:18.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  來份干筍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:22.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…小萌老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏  是賣什麼的小攤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又遲到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在幹些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:43.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為第一學期的評價還沒整理好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:47.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那種玩意不是早該在暑假之前就應該做完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:52.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你就不用來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你要在今天之內弄完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:57.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:01.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  下一次喝酒你請客
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:21.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到這個時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡做的事情…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太過注重大招了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:42.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有最好要注意一下攻守平衡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便發動的攻擊還不如不攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能換我玩一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:53.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果長按開始鍵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓後再…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:03.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:07.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  不過我也完全不會用這個角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:09.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:17.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自己喜歡的遊戲的秘籍的話  一定會想知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:20.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個角色還挺可愛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎  身為警備員卻做這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校的工作也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是想要久違地放縱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:40.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  看看我的功力有沒有退步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小萌老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉川老師陷入緊急狀況了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉川老師她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JAMIE…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JAMIE的結局很燃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要錯過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經喝不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的緊急狀況就是指這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼從這時間就開始喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底喝了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人稍微喝了五六升吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵裝老師  你開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你覺得今天是怎樣的一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:56.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再之前又是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能並不怎麼開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作也很忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都過得很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這座城市裏生活著各種各樣的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:19.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中還有將我家的屋頂給吹跑了的讓人頭疼的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  屋頂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:29.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我愛著包括那個學生在內的所有學生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵裝老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是從I地區到L地區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:50.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分頭干吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就從L地區開始巡視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁十足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是哪裏的使魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(382,328)\fs18\fsp-1}Agathion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪裏的學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是學生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是修女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:19.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說  你掉的甜甜圈被清掃機器人給回收了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:25.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當麻告訴我  這個國家存在著名為「三秒規則」的偉大法則哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得這規則對馬路不適用的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  把我的甜甜圈還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:38.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  這位客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:50.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  那孩子非要把店裏所有的漢堡包給買下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:55.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你是哪裏的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧之丘女子學院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在是自由之身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由之身…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你為什麼要點那麼多漢堡包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人難以忘懷的味道  所以要全部買下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  絕對不能氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:23.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:28.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像把項鏈給弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,項鏈？  有什麼特徵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:33.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面放著照片那種
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吊墜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:39.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能放照片的項鏈是叫這個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  現在的孩子不這麼說麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,項鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是在這附近弄丟的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來幫你一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地震
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:11.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  剛才是不是地震了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有搖麼  你多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:16.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼  太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你是哪裏的學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一個吊墜都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:45.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的在努力麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好遲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JAMIE使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可不能輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:24.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨臂撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:34.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:38.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有著大宮JAMIE這樣的稱號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:45.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦  1比1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場決戰絕對要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:14.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不比當年了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  久違地燃了一把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大宮JAMIE嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  被聽到…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:35.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  你後來真的把JAMIE線給爆機了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:36.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:41.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激掌10還會不會出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:43.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的  都是那麼老的遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有的話  下次可要報一箭之仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會期待著的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大宮JAMIE小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把那個忘掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裏就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:10.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行  都過了完全放學時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能放任一個中學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:15.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:16.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:23.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:32.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊  也不聯絡我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不來的話就說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:39.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是很擔心的呦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不至於…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嘛  今天是你請客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}大叔  今天就多來些貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:47.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  別跟我說你忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:47.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:56.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉校了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:57.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假裏突然就轉校了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:06.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他轉去的學校叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:08.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜草學院中學部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜草學院是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:13.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取名再怎麼草率也該有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:17.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜草在英語中不是weed嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遊戲製作公司weed旗下的學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,weed？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:26.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前通過一款叫做激掌的遊戲紅極一時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有聽說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:33.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是一所培養遊戲製作人的學校嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:37.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說專業性知識要到高中時才會教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼會去weed那種走下坡路的公司呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:45.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家公司製作的遊戲中也不乏我喜愛的作品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為初春是狂熱者嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}我也沒那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  看著真難受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.62,0:21:50.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:52.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:59.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  到了完全放學時間可得乖乖回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:00.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要加油嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:09.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:12.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  接下來是E地區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:12.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是F啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:14.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到JAN的話就會想到划拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:34.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是麻將吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:37.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的前世是冉·阿讓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:39.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JAN  啦啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}大叔  來份燉紅薯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:35.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}大叔  來份醋拌卷蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:38.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}大叔  來份味噌豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:39.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}大叔…

